The premier club football competition in Africa is held annually by the Confederation of African Football (CAF) and features the top performing champions in their respective leagues."Mamelodi Sundowns carry the hopes of South Africa as they compete for the Star of this competition in African football. We wish them well ahead of the match and are certain that they will bring the trophy home " said Zuma.Orlando Pirates FC is the only other South African team that has lifted the trophy in 1995. - TMG Digital